{ Prophylaxis against Bg5. If Black develops the light-squared bishop instead as is natural, it's much to his detriment since then we get Bg5 in   10...Bf5  11.Bg5  h6  12.Bh4  Be7  13.Re1  or   10...Bf5  11.Bg5  h6  12.Bh4  Na5  13.Bd3  Bxd3  14.Qxd3  Nc6  15.Ne4 }
